Name: TypeOfDevelopmentActivityGroup
Description: A generic element for specifying a reason for a Development Activities Group. Note that this element can contain either a term from a controlled vocabulary list or a textual description.

Name: DevelopmentActivityGroupName
Description: A name for the DevelopmentActivityGroup. May be expressed in multiple languages. Repeat the element to express names with different content, for example different names for different systems.

Name: Label
Description: A display label for the DevelopmentActivityGroup. Supports multiple language versions of the same content as well as optional formatting of the content. Repeat for labels with different content, for example, labels with differing length limitations.

Name: Description
Description: A description of the DevelopmentActivityGroup. Supports multiple language versions of the same content as well as optional formatting of the content.

Name: UniverseReference
Description: Reference to the universe statement describing the persons or other objects to which the contents of this group pertain.

Name: ConceptReference
Description: Reference to the concept expressed by the objects in this group.

Name: Subject
Description: If subjects are listed for this group, it is strongly recommended that the subjects listed also be found in the TopicalCoverage element for the parent packaging element when this group is included directly or by reference in a module containing a coverage element. Use of subject at the group level allows for associating objects as a type of subject based group or to identify subject characteristics of a reusable group of objects.

Name: Keyword
Description: If keywords are listed for this group, it is strongly recommended that the keywords listed also be found in the TopicalCoverage element for the parent packaging element when this group is included directly or by reference in a module containing a coverage element. Use of keyword at the group level allows for associating objects as a type of keyword based group or to identify keyword characteristics of a reusable group of objects.

Name: DevelopmentActivityReference
Description: Reference to a constituent DevelopmentActivity for inclusion in the group. TypeOfObject should be ContentReviewActivity, TranslationActivity, or PretestActivity.

Name: DevelopmentActivityGroupReference
Description: Reference to constituent Development Activity group. This allows for nesting of processing instruction groups. TypeOfObject should be DevelopmentActivityGroup.

Name: IsOrdered
Description: If set to "true" indicates that the content of the group is ordered as it appears within the XML structure.
